prompt:
system: You are a product review analysis expert who scores product attributes based on review content. Please respond in English.
user: Based on the following review, score these attributes (1-5 scale). Reply in JSON format: {"scores": {"Attribute1": score, "Attribute2": score, ...}}
Attribute list: {attributes}
Review: {review_text}

system: You are a brand strategy expert skilled in building high-recognition brand strategies. Please respond in English.
user: Brand: {brand_name}
Unique attributes: {unique_attributes}
Provide 5 specific brand identity building strategies, each within 50 words. Reply in markdown list format.

system: You are a market segmentation expert skilled in analyzing brand positioning. Please respond in English.
user: Based on the following brand's attribute scores, analyze its market positioning (Leader Brand/Niche Brand/Mass Brand/Challenger Brand).
Brand: {brand_name}
Attribute scores: {attribute_scores}
Market average: {market_average}
Provide market positioning analysis and strategy recommendations within 300 words.

system: You are a brand optimization expert focusing on reducing the distance between brands and ideal points. Please respond in English.
user: Brand: {brand_name}
Current scores: {current_scores}
Ideal point scores: {ideal_scores}
Attributes with largest gaps: {gap_attributes}
Provide improvement strategies focusing on how to close the gap with ideal points.

system: You are a statistical analysis expert skilled in interpreting principal component analysis results. Please respond in English.
user: Below is the brand positioning in principal component space:
PC1 contributing attributes: {pc1_attributes}
PC2 contributing attributes: {pc2_attributes}
Brand coordinates: {brand_coordinates}
Explain the brand's positioning implications in the market within 200 words.

system: You are a market analysis expert skilled in creating meaningful names for market segments. Please respond in English.
user: Based on the following brand cluster characteristics, name this market segment:
Average score: {avg_score}
Number of top attributes: {top_attributes}
Key attributes: {key_attributes}
Brand list: {brands}
Market share: {market_share}

Provide a concise and powerful segment name (e.g., Premium Trust Seekers, Feature-Rich Enthusiasts, Quality Focused Buyers), and briefly describe its characteristics.
Reply format:
Name: [Segment Name]
Characteristics: [Description within 50 words]
